description: El Charrua Grill & Catering is serving the foodies of Houston some amazingly authentic  Uruguayan cuisine. This family-run truck is serving up traditional recipes like Choripán, piled high with tasty chorizo, and other juicy meats and fresh veggie toppings. You’ll also find BBQ, empanadas, savory pies, and so much more.  If you’re hungry for something real tasty for your next meal or next big party, call on El Charrua Grill & Catering to roll in the deliciousness.
name: El Charrua Grill & Catering
